data.description: Welcome to 7083 E Mt Hope Hwy, a stunning house nestled on a spacious 2.5-acre lot in Grand Ledge. This charming property offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. With 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, there is plenty of space for you and your loved ones to thrive. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the elegance of cathedral ceilings and an abundance of natural light pouring in through ample windows, doors, and skylights, creating an inviting and airy atmosphere throughout the home. The primary bedroom boasts an ensuite bathroom for added privacy and convenience. Enjoy the serenity of your own private sun deck, perfect for soaking up the sun or sipping your morning coffee while overlooking the well-maintained landscape adorned with mature trees. The walk-out basement has potential to add additional living space with plenty of storage. Cozy up on chilly evenings next to one of the two fireplaces found within this home. The attached garage offers ample parking space for two vehicles, ensuring convenience and protection from the elements. The formal dining room provides an elegant setting for hosting dinner parties or enjoying meals with family and friends. The entrance foyer adds a touch of sophistication to this already impressive property.  There is a partially new roof, mechanicals and some doors and windows have been replaced.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your dream home.  Measurements are approximate BATVIA.  Schedule your showing today!
